name: nytimes
text: Over 20 Navajo voters rode three hours on horseback to cast their ballots in #election2020 on Tuesday. Community leaders feared widespread disenfranchisement in Navajo Nation, where mail can take weeks to arrive — if it gets there at all. https://t.co/RRKhLINLBX https://t.co/KSOCAoPNwv
